
About the job

\U0001f5c2 We’re Hiring: Data Analyst (Entry / Junior)
 \U0001f552 Employment Type: Full-Time
 \U0001f4bc Level: Entry-Level / Junior
We are seeking a detail-oriented and analytical Data Analyst to join our team. In this role, you will be responsible for collecting, processing, and analyzing data to support business decisions and uncover actionable insights.
You will work closely with cross-functional teams to transform data into meaningful reports and visualizations. This is an excellent opportunity for someone looking to build a strong foundation in data analytics and grow within a data-driven environment.
\U0001f3af Key Responsibilities
Collect, clean, and analyze data from various sources.
Develop and maintain reports, dashboards, and visualizations.
Identify trends, patterns, and insights to support business decisions.
Assist in building and optimizing data models and datasets.
Work with stakeholders to understand data requirements and objectives.
Ensure data accuracy, consistency, and integrity.
Support ad hoc analysis and reporting requests.
Document data processes and maintain data dictionaries.
\u2705 Requirements
Bachelor’s degree in Data Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Computer Science, or a related field (or equivalent experience).
Basic knowledge of data analysis concepts and techniques.
Proficiency in Microsoft Excel; familiarity with SQL is preferred.
Experience with data visualization tools (e.g., Power BI, Tableau) is a plus.
Basic programming knowledge (Python or R) is an advantage.
Strong analytical thinking and problem-solving skills.
Attention to detail and ability to work with large datasets.
Good communication skills to present data insights clearly.
Internship or project experience in data analysis is preferred but not required.
\U0001f31f What We Offer
A collaborative and data-driven work environment.
Opportunities to work on real-world data projects.
Career growth and continuous learning opportunities.
Mentorship from experienced data professionals.
Competitive salary and benefits package. 

